{"tid":2038232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃日華老婆梁潔華器官衰竭離世　終年59歲","createTime":"2020-05-27T12:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T21:28:03.000Z","uid":228995,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"58c44203173cbd4ca2d06e3aeb948dc7bc334153","tid":2038232,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"黃日華老婆梁潔華昨日不敵病魔，於醫院離世，終年59歲。有報道指黃日華已確認消息，更指太太是因器官衰竭安詳離世，感謝醫護的照顧，將會與女兒黃芷晴處理太太後事。<br />\n<br />\n其實梁潔華在2013年已被診斷有急性骨髓性白血病，在2015年承認病情， 2018年女兒黃芷晴稱媽媽接受二骨髓移植手術並手術成功，但依然經常要出入醫院。"},{"pid":"d6ca8a893359a7a0ba1cf28185a80e8226be6b75","tid":2038232,"uid":37146,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"黃定藍?"},{"pid":"46df9439e007127900b4b148d230ee1951a8c67b","tid":2038232,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"一瞬間以為黃子華"},{"pid":"ff092ebb8c01d01d50f856169fb3dfceae4728fc","tid":2038232,"uid":228995,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d6ca8a893359a7a0ba1cf28185a80e8226be6b75","tid":2038232,"uid":37146,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"黃定藍?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"唔知，剩係知個女幾正"},{"pid":"64a852f332700fd2e5e3aeef18816835e1df29a8","tid":2038232,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2838c76b426d9197f1dadca97f62f885d1868031","tid":2038232,"uid":349872,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"46df9439e007127900b4b148d230ee1951a8c67b","tid":2038232,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"一瞬間以為黃子華"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"黃子華鬼有老婆呀，玩膠都唔係呢個時候啦，兒登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c5db00982284a9ba1b163d6331ccaa03c0a03c","tid":2038232,